{"tid":2468210,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選最好嘅光之美少女","createTime":"2021-03-30T10:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T13:46:34.000Z","uid":305269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7794b9a07f0f45b707cdad226990454c4508a464","tid":2468210,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1frhEn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1frhEn.jpg&h=ddf321b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無印劇情最好，D笑位又正<br />\n二期都唔差，但冇一期咁突出<br />\nBTW，莎莎嗰啊爸日本配音係Dio<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZdPZTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZdPZTM.jpg&h=12c36bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSplash Star就係垃圾，翻炒無印<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPkCpnr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPkCpnr.jpg&h=d46e85f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYes呢一代劇情都ok，但係我好好奇點解女主鍾意咗隻畜生，同畜生嘅智商點解變咗人就上升，變番畜生又跌番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩期都差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKoo4pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKoo4pi.jpg&h=422df321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFresh呢一代有個有趣位，就係喺反派嘅國家係極權國家，會監察國民，喺子供向節目入面夠薑放咁黑暗嘅元素入去都幾大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOhk6E8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOhk6E8.jpg&h=42485500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nheartcatch角色好得意，畫風同Doremi好似，因為係一樣嘅製作班底，馬越嘉彥、山田隆司同埋長峰達也，故仔都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a70ZCO7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa70ZCO7.jpg&h=4bf0a845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsuite有蘿莉先加50分，劇情麻麻<br />\n但係疑似本來嘅Cure Muse唔係蘿莉而係紫色嘅pretty cure，唔知咩原因先換咗蘿莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcE0nhC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcE0nhC.jpg&h=53ae712e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsmile角色幾得意，劇情零記憶點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNU7MLg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNU7MLg.jpg&h=e4d9b43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ndokidoki角色最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合上面幾套，heartcatch係暫時平均嚟講最好嘅作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後嗰D已經冇睇，有冇ching可以補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dce1df5884a88d541cba48d56aa94966dac925","tid":2468210,"uid":203393,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"第一代打戲最正"},{"pid":"84f39367f368a8486f2388f4a42c47f6edac761a","tid":2468210,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9dce1df5884a88d541cba48d56aa94966dac925","tid":2468210,"uid":203393,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"第一代打戲最正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"打擊感好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621f92dfd3fee44fcdeb305f3739a9ec7c3224b6","tid":2468210,"uid":150609,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"Heartcatch"},{"pid":"cd3522c3bd76f4cabed6d8db334a297690722be0","tid":2468210,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"開心殘廁 易裸射唔多"},{"pid":"e727dc7a4d3bacd6b235b64c2ceb746f2c440453","tid":2468210,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,